message.body: Hey Toren, were u able to do a test
￼Hi hunter, so the test today went OK. Your outer most line did not register well however. You can see how it cut off some detail. I will try some different registration options tomorrow
I think Stephen had the same problem when he tried this cut on our lasers before
Yeah I may have to go bigger unfortunately bc I already have the frames made
￼Here is a closeup. Some lines I think are too close together for it to stay together
So yeah maybe bigger would be better
I could also alter the drawing in illustrator but I don't have time to do that right now with getting all of he rest of my work ready to show
Also, on some of the curves, you can see the laser cuts a little jagged- I think with a file this detailed this is unfortunately the best our lasers can
do. Might be better larger.
If you think of a different size let me know and I can try that
I can also try the smaller size on the paper you supplied- might turn out better.. Your call
Can I bring you some paper to run one at 2x scale
Sure
I'm available the next few days. I could drop it off at penn
Cool. I'm at Penn tomorrow most of the day. If Thurs is better I can make it work too
I can drop it off tomorrow
Cool
What time do you get there?
8 in the morning
Ok see you then
Cool
I can't make til later today
What time are you thinking, turns out I have to leave at 1230 today
You can always swing by and drop material off and the other guys can stash it for me
Running larger size now, separated outline and some of the other internal areas. will send pics of results.
